-- Kenya Reinsuranace Financial-Strength Rating Maintained at B+ by A.M. Best
-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 2010-11-25T05:26:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-25/kenya-reinsuranace-financial-strength-rating-maintained-at-b-by-a-m-best.html
Kenya Reinsurance Corp., a state-
owned reinsurer, had its financial-strength rating maintained at
B+ and issuer credit rating at BBB- by A.M. Best Co.  “The outlook for both ratings remains stable,” the
ratings firm in an e-mailed report late yesterday in Nairobi,
the capital. “The ratings reflect Kenya Re’s strong level of
risk-adjusted capitalisation and good local business profile”.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  